}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== Appears to also be sold as the [[Belkin F4G0500|'''F4G0500''']] (UPC + ASIN in this entry are for the F4G0500)
From a F5D5131-5v5 unit with a S/N of '''14153S55513115'''... *"270-NB0-FS105A002B0 REV:B" and a date code of '''4911''' is silkscreened on the board. **This seems to indicate '''Intelligent Technology''' / '''Netronix''' manufacture *All radial capacitors on the board are '''ChengX''' branded.
